_sText:
Hey

This is a dev texture deathrun map with 15 traps. Players spawn with knives only and terrorists get a speed boost to help them keep up.

****************

Features:

> HDR

> No real easter eggs besides two flashbangs. It is a FAIR map.

> No hidden traps. Even new players can see where traps will be.

> Made with cool looking dev (developer) textures

****************

Hope all of you out there enjoy the map. It's great fun to play.


UPDATE to Beta 4 25/7/10:

> Last trap made harder
> Can no longer walk on sills
> Moved second flash
> Increased CT spawns and reduced T spawns
